desc: Wilow is a premium level design brand for people who are highly interested in conscious fashion and lifestyle. All our accessories and clothes are sustainably made in the EU and designed in Helsinki, Finland.

layout.text: Our collaboration “Art on Fashion” is an exclusive collection, where Stiofán Grego´s art is painted to an Italian silk. Stiofán´s vibe is raw, untamed and channels the inspiration of true street culture.
